  "texts": [
    "Fig. 3 Paper and patent mapping (1990s and 2010s)",
    "Regarding changes over time, as the number of research papers increases with respect to the total number of documents, an expansion of research papers in technical fields can be observed (overlapping area of red and blue).",
    "This trend is particularly notable in the fields of chemistry/materials (compounds, metallic materials).",
    "It was also evident that research papers had been published in fields such as electronics devices and image displays, which were previously only covered mainly by patents.",
